OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,FXabi Alonso urged Chelsea to develop a
OL,7,F"hunger" for victory and revealed he
OL,8,Fhas spoken to midfielder Enzo
OL,9,FFernandez in his first press
OL,10,Fconference as Blues boss at Stamford
OL,11,FBridge.
OL,13,FThe 44-year-old also shared his views
OL,14,Fon the ongoing World Cup and his
OL,15,Fmemories from his own involvement in
OL,16,FSpain's victory in 2010, as well as
OL,17,Fthe club's plans for their late-
OL,18,Freturning players from the global
OL,19,Fshowpiece.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
