FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,FThe former Real Madrid boss was more
OL,7,Fkeen to discuss his philosophy rather
OL,8,Fthan make any predictions about how
OL,9,FChelsea might fare in his first season
OL,10,Fin charge but insisted European
OL,11,Fqualification was among the targets.
OL,13,F"For sure that's a goal," he said.
OL,14,F"But to reach that goal, you need to
OL,15,Fdo many right things and to be part of
OL,16,Fthat process, how do we want to play,
OL,17,Fhow we want to see ourselves, how we
OL,18,Fwant to approach a game wherever we go.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@YO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,F"That's my job. That's why I am really
OL,7,Flooking forward to having the whole
OL,8,Fsquad. At the moment we have some
OL,9,Fbids, but early days so far.
OL,11,F"But for sure, we want to be there and
OL,12,Ftime will tell. But we are ambitious
OL,13,Fand we in Chelsea need to share that
OL,14,Fenergy, that ambition, as well as that
OL,15,Fhunger to want to have success."
OL,17,FAlonso also insisted Chelsea were keen
OL,18,Fto hang onto Fernandez, whose future
OL,19,Fwith the club has been in doubt this
OL,20,Fsummer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@`O]
