PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Real Madrid denied
OL,7,Fholding an interest in signing the
OL,8,FChelsea midfielder, whose Argentina
OL,9,Fside will face England during
OL,10,FWednesday night's World Cup semi-final.
OL,12,F"Yes, we have spoken," Alonso
OL,13,Fconfirmed. "But as you can understand,
OL,14,Fwhat we have spoken about remains
OL,15,Fprivate. But yes, we have spoken."
OL,17,FAsked if he would like Fernandez to
OL,18,Fremain at Stamford Bridge, Alonso
OL,19,Freplied: "Yes."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@VO]uD@LOUwD@bO]{D@JOU{D@OO]
