PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,FFernandez is one of four Chelsea
OL,7,Fplayers still involved in the World
OL,8,FCup alongside England duo Reece James
OL,9,Fand Trevoh Chalobah and France's Malo
OL,10,FGusto.
OL,12,FFormer Liverpool midfielder Alonso was
OL,13,Freminded that Antonio Conte was the
OL,14,Flast Chelsea boss to lead a side to a
OL,15,FPremier League trophy when he did so a
OL,16,Fdecade ago in the 2016-17 season.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
