OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,FThey have employed a carousel of
OL,7,Fbosses since, including just three and
OL,8,Fa half months in the dugout for Liam
OL,9,FRosenior, his predecessor as permanent
OL,10,FBlues boss.
OL,12,FThe Spaniard, who signed a four-year
OL,13,Fdeal to join the west London club,
OL,14,Fdanced around the subject when asked
OL,15,Fwhether he was confident he will be
OL,16,Fgiven enough time to build a team that
OL,17,Fcould challenge for the title.
OL,19,FHowever, he added: "What I am sure is
OL,20,Fthat we have the ambition to want to
OL,21,Fwin a lot of games, to be competitive.
OL,26,@{D@TOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784024302
OL,3,CNew Chelsea boss Xabi Alonso demands
OL,4,Cteam show 'hunger' for success
OL,6,F"We need to take important decisions,
OL,7,Fwe need to build strong principles and
OL,8,Fa strong mentality and culture in the
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,F"Time will tell. I'm not going to say
OL,12,Fwhat will happen in May. For me, it's
OL,13,Fabsolutely too early to say that, but
OL,14,FI am confident, I am optimistic that
OL,15,Fwe can have a great season."
